# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Editor
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Secrets
.env

# Test logs and coverage (local only)
logs/*.log
logs/coverage/

# Test dependencies (local only)
tests/node_modules/

# Misc
*.log
logs/

# Session docs
#docs/

# Local-only issue tracker (synced to GitLab via API when token is provided;
# until then this file is the single source of truth and stays off the web)
docs/issues-pending.md

# Local-only DM/invitation working list — contains stage names, contact slugs,
# DM templates. Stays off both the deploy and the open repo.
docs/einladungen-zu-versenden.md

# Local-only drafts — anything in docs/ ending in -DRAFT.md stays off the web.
# Useful for politically sensitive pieces that need to be written down for
# alignment with Stefan but are not ready to ship.
docs/*-DRAFT.md

# Local-only e-mail drafts (Thunderbird .eml templates etc.).
# These contain mailto-style envelopes, addressee mail addresses,
# personal cover-letter text — they are working files, not shipped content.
docs/email-drafts/

# Photos of private persons stay local. A self-published stage name
# releases the name, not the face — see the "Photos and likenesses"
# clause in the Privacy section of CLAUDE.md. Drop photos in
# docs/_private/ (gitignored below) until an explicit photo release
# is on file. Image extensions in docs/ are blanket-ignored as a
# belt-and-suspenders.
docs/_private/
docs/*.jpg
docs/*.jpeg
docs/*.png
docs/*.heic
docs/*.webp

# Imported artifacts from other Claude sessions / Anthropic web app exports.
# Stefan's parallel Claude work — material that may feed into /journeys/ etc.
# Stays local, gets reviewed, then explicitly integrated by Stefan & Claude.
docs/imported-artifacts/

# Session logs (root-level)
SESSION-*.md

# Per-session summaries written by Claude at end-of-session.
# Local memory only — not part of the deploy and not shared.
docs/sessions/

# Scratch test scripts and debug artifacts
tests/burger-*.js
tests/firefox-*.js
tests/debug-*.js
tests/diag-*.js
tests/show-*.js
tests/screenshots/
tests/wip/
